summary.description:
Today, a bit warmer for the feels like temperature (up 6.2°C) and outside temperature (up 5.6°C) and more moisture-laden outside humidity (up 6%).

Compared to today, yesterday also had noticeable differences in cloud levels (up 369 m).

The past week and month had observable variation in cloud levels (up 696 m), light levels (up 4008 lux), dew point temperature (down 1.6°C), and inside temperature (up 1.9°C) when compared to today.
